// BoseRV Module 1 Test Program
// Assembled RISC-V instructions in hex (little-endian word format)
//
// Instruction | Hex        | Assembly
// ============|============|================================
// ADDI x1,x0,5   | 00500093 | x1 = 5
// ADDI x2,x0,20  | 01400113 | x2 = 20
// ADD  x3,x1,x2  | 002081b3 | x3 = x1 + x2 = 25
// ADDI x4,x0,100 | 06400213 | x4 = 100 (used as base address)
// SW   x3,0(x4)  | 00322023 | mem[100] = x3 = 25
// LW   x5,0(x4)  | 00022283 | x5 = mem[100] = 25
// BEQ  x3,x5,+8  | 00518463 | if(x3==x5) PC+=8 (skip next 2)
// ADDI x6,x0,255 | 0ff00313 | SKIPPED: x6 = 255 (if branch works)
// ADDI x7,x0,255 | 0ff00393 | SKIPPED: x7 = 255 (if branch works)
// ADDI x8,x0,170 | 0aa00413 | x8 = 0xAA (branch lands here)
// (infinite loop or NOP after here)
00500093
01400113
002081b3
06400213
00322023
00022283
00518663
0ff00313
0ff00393
0aa00413